mpensation committee which she chaired from  to  of joann stores inc a national specialty retailer of craft sewing and decorating products ms raff graduated from boston university with a bachelor of business administration degree and from drexel university with a masters of business administration ms raff is well known throughout the retail industry and brings to the board of directors her experience and perspective as an outstanding merchant and multistore retail executive the board expects to benefit from ms raffs extensive knowledge of the retail industry and her valuable insight on how we can best serve our retail partners ms raffs current and previous service on other boards also provides important perspectives on key corporate governance matters source helen of troy limited on    sign up for equilar atlas and view beryl b raffs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like beryl b raff more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in beryl b raffs network and community follow changes in beryl b raffs employment and moneyinmotion connect with beryl b raff through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example beryl b raff beryl b raffs connections  sign up now to view beryl b raffs  connections » frank a newman board member jabil inc tracey t travis executive vice president and chief financial officer the est�e lauder companies inc jonathan d sokoloff former board member whole foods market inc bonnie w gwin vice chairman and managing director of board practice north america heidrick  struggles international inc scott s cowen lead independent director forest city realty trust inc ira j gumberg former board member mellon financial dennis a mullahy executive vice president supply chain and information technology the michaels companies inc charles m sonsteby vice chairman the michaels companies inc monte e ford board mem