ewelry and finally senior vice president and general merchandise manager for macy’s east bridge and fine jewelry and lingerie   in  the women’s jewelry association named her to its lifetime hall of fame and in  the american ort jewelry industry presented her with their community achievement award beryl is the  and  recipient of the uja – federation of ny – diamond jewelry and watch division’s “leadership award of excellence” in  beryl was inducted into national jeweler’s retailer hall of fame in the majors category beryl serves on the board of group  automotive a fortune  company and the national association of corporate directors heartland chapter she also served on the board of joann stores for  years until the company was taken private    beryl is active within the jewelry industry serving on the executive board of the jewelers vigilance committee and the advisory board for jewelers’ circular keystone  under her leadership helzberg has focused its philanthropic efforts on the make a wish foundation  beryl is honored to be a member of the national board of make a wish foundation beryl and her late husband barry have one child edward    thank you for reviewing my bio and being a helzberg diamonds valued customer sincerely beryl b raff chairman and ceo beryl raff image gallery   organizationsaffilliations beryl raff  group  automotive beryl raff  iwf dallas   beryl raff newsupdates   helzberg diamonds ceo gives candid look at her career journey  may   when beryl raff looks back on her journey it seems surreal at times she still thinks how did all of that happen her keys to success have been a little luck and following her passion she said read more ags recognizes beryl raff  lifetime achievement award  august   new yorkberyl raff howard hauben and three members of the bromberg family were honored tuesday night at the american gem society’s th annual circle of distinction dinner held at the plaza hotel raff chairman and ceo of kansas city mobased helzberg diamonds wa